        "timestamp": "2019-11-29 11:25:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> i have made some changes to https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Robot+Framework+Development+Guide that should cover your commit. If you would like to link from there in the read me that would be good i think\n\nThank you for the guidelines\n\nPlease clarify - would you like me to:\n1) replace this patch with a new one providing just a link (in the README.md file) to the Wiki page or\n2) convert Wiki page content to Markdown, put it to the README.md and leave a link to the repo on the Wiki page or\n3) convert Wiki page content to RST, put it to the repo (e.g. integration/docs/docs_robot.rst or a new one testsuite/docs/contributing.rst) and have it published on docs.onap.org?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
