        "timestamp": "2019-12-02 17:35:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> i dont know - i dont have a preferred method, and my main concern was not to duplicate the text. What is the method the rest of onap uses?\n\nI asked @kopasiak who has biggest experience with various ONAP projects from people I know.\n\nI was told that Wiki is meant to bootstrap/sketch out basics (since it's easy to collaborate) and then it is recommended to migrate the content to docs.onap.org (option #3).\n\nLet me know what you think",
        "patchset_number": 1
